work is corroborated by hardware experiments\nthat are based on a hysteresis enabled, modulo ADC testbed comprising\noff-the-shelf electronic components. Thus, by capitalizing on a collaboration\nbetween hardware and algorithms, our paper enables an end-to-end pipeline for\nHDR sampling allowing more flexible hardware implementations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Nov 2021 18:10:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-16"}
