t in different regions or dynamical\nregimes. This is direct observational evidence for the three-dimensional\nthermo-chemical stratification of an exoplanet atmosphere derived from\nhigh-resolution ground-based spectroscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Nov 2021 19:00:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 30 Jan 2022 11:18:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-01"}
