Waals materials can vary significantly depending\non stoichiometry, defect types and concentration, and possibly environmental\nand substrate effects. In view of this finding, local probing of nanoribbon\nproperties with TERS becomes essential to understanding such low-dimensional\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Nov 2021 22:54:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-29"}
